{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotter\/addannotation:"]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter"]]},"sections":[],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"addAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"addAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","title":"addAnnotation:","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapSnapshotter(im)addAnnotation:","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}]},"abstract":[{"text":"Adds an annotation to the snapshotter.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"addAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"id<MLNAnnotation>","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"annotation","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The annotation object to add to the receiver. This object"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"must conform to the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. The snapshotter retains the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation object."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"annotation"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":""},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" objects cannot be added to the snapshotter at this time."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Any multipoint, multipolyline, multipolygon, shape or point collection"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that is specified is silently ignored."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside","name":"Note","style":"note"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter\/addAnnotation:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotOptions":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotOptions","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapSnapshotOptions"}],"title":"MLNMapSnapshotOptions","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotoptions","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The options to use when creating images with the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotation","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPointCollection":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpointcollection","abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"disconnected vertices, specified as ","type":"text"},{"code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" instances. The","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"points in the collection may be related but are not connected spatially. For","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"example, you could use a point collection to represent all the trees in an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"orchard.","type":"text"}],"title":"MLNPointCollection","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNPointCollection","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","title":"MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolyline":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMultiPolyline"}],"title":"MLNMultiPolyline","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolyline","abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"polylines. For example, you could use a multipolyline shape to represent both","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"sides of a divided highway (dual carriageway), excluding the median (central","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"reservation): each carriageway would be a distinct ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" object.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPolyline":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNPolyline"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpolyline","role":"symbol","title":"MLNPolyline","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of two or more vertices,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"specified as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"type":"text","text":" instances, and the line segments that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"connect them. For example, you could use an polyline to represent a road or the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"path along which something moves."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshot":{"role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"An image generated by a snapshotter object.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNMapSnapshot","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshot","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapSnapshot"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshot"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate":{"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotterdelegate","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate"}],"title":"MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Optional methods about significant events when creating a snapshot using an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter"},{"type":"text","text":" object."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotter/addAnnotation:":{"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addAnnotation:"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Adds an annotation to the snapshotter.","type":"text"}],"title":"addAnnotation:","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter\/addAnnotation:","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotter\/addannotation:","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"addAnnotation:"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotter":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" generates static raster images of the map. Each snapshot"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"image depicts a portion of a map defined by an "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotOptions","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you provide. The snapshotter generates an "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshot","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"asynchronously, calling "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate"},{"type":"text","text":" methods if defined, then"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"passing it into a completion handler once tiles and other resources needed for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the snapshot are finished loading."}],"role":"symbol","title":"MLNMapSnapshotter","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapSnapshotter","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotter"}}}